sequenceDiagram
    actor Patient
    participant Doctor
    participant CaseRecord
    participant Episode

    Patient->>Doctor: Present new problem
    Doctor->>CaseRecord: Open new Case
    Note over CaseRecord,Episode: Episode is created within the newly opened Case
    CaseRecord->>Episode: Open new Episode within Case